'Exercising my Faith in the Marketplace' is a book that enables corporate people to understand their place in the Christian Kingdom and carry out their leadership skills.The writer, Caroline Mbunacho, works for General Electric and is based in the US. She has put together a must-read for every person who is in the corporate world.The launch happened at Sarova Panafric. It was full of corporate attendees and family to experience the birth of new ideas to enable push them through career growth.